data.description: Charm meets convenience in this delightful single-family abode!  This beautifully crafted KB home features a gourmet kitchen with double oven, electric cooktop, granite countertops, raised bartop kitchen island, 42'' upper cabinets and Moen hardware.  The functional floorplan gives both space and an openess with energy star LED surface lights in family room and kitchen.  The installation of the KB Smart Tech package allows for wired security and smart thermostat, and flat panel conduit for TV. French doors lead to the extended patio and backyard with limitless possibilities which oversees over a quarter acre and backs up to creek.  Prime location to NAS Jax, shopping, downtown Jax and easy access to highway.  This home offers the ideal blend of suburban living and urban accessibility. Shed does convey with properties.  Seller will consider closing cost.
